t" width="1100"/></div><div class="mb-5" data-type="image"><img alt="Nervous system control of heart rate 2" class="ContentBlock_figure__6whpf" data-nimg="1" decoding="async" height="662" sizes="(max-width: 320px) 320w, (max-width: 640px) 640w, (max-width: 960px) 960w, (max-width: 1280px) 1280w, 1920w" src="Nervous-system-control-of-heart-rate-2.png" srcset="https://cdn.savemyexams.com/cdn-cgi/image/f=auto,width=16/https://cdn.savemyexams.com/uploads/2022/01/Nervous-system-control-of-heart-rate-2.png 16w, https://cdn.savemyexams.com/cdn-cgi/image/f=auto,width=32/https://cdn.savemyexams.com/uploads/2022/01/Nervous-system-control-of-heart-rate-2.png 32w, https://cdn.savemyexams.com/cdn-cgi/image/f=auto,width=48/https://cdn.savemyexams.com/uploads/2022/01/Nervous-system-control-of-heart-rate-2.png 48w, https://cdn.savemyexams.com/cdn-cgi/image/f=auto,width=64/https://cdn.savemyexams.com/uploads/2022/01/Nervous-system-control-of-heart-rate-2.png 64w, https://cdn.savemyexams.com/cdn-cgi/image/f=auto,width=96/https://cdn.savemyexams.com/uploads/2022/01/Nervous-system-control-of-heart-rate-2.png 96w, https://cdn.savemyexams.com/cdn-cgi/image/f=auto,width=128/https://cdn.savemyexams.com/uploads/2022/01/Nervous-system-control-of-heart-rate-2.png 128w, https://cdn.savemyexams.com/cdn-cgi/image/f=auto,width=256/https://cdn.savemyexams.com/uploads/2022/01/Nervous-system-control-of-heart-rate-2.png 256w, https://cdn.savemyexams.com/cdn-cgi/image/f=auto,width=384/https://cdn.savemyexams.com/uploads/2022/01/Nervous-system-control-of-heart-rate-2.png 384w, https://cdn.savemyexams.com/cdn-cgi/image/f=auto,width=640/https://cdn.savemyexams.com/uploads/2022/01/Nervous-system-control-of-heart-rate-2.png 640w, https://cdn.savemyexams.com/cdn-cgi/image/f=auto,width=750/https://cdn.savemyexams.com/uploads/2022/01/Nervous-system-control-of-heart-rate-2.png 750w, https://cdn.savemyexams.com/cdn-cgi/image/f=auto,width=828/https://cdn.savemyexams.com/uploads/2022/01/Nervous-system-control-of-heart-rate-2.png 828w, https://cdn.savemyexams.com/cdn-cgi/image/f=auto,width=1080/https://cdn.savemyexams.com/uploads/2022/01/Nervous-system-control-of-heart-rate-2.png 1080w, https://cdn.savemyexams.com/cdn-cgi/image/f=auto,width=1200/https://cdn.savemyexams.com/uploads/2022/01/Nervous-system-control-of-heart-rate-2.png 1200w, https://cdn.savemyexams.com/cdn-cgi/image/f=auto,width=1920/https://cdn.savemyexams.com/uploads/2022/01/Nervous-system-control-of-heart-rate-2.png 1920w, https://cdn.savemyexams.com/cdn-cgi/image/f=auto,width=2048/https://cdn.savemyexams.com/uploads/2022/01/Nervous-system-control-of-heart-rate-2.png 2048w, https://cdn.savemyexams.com/cdn-cgi/image/f=auto,width=3840/https://cdn.savemyexams.com/uploads/2022/01/Nervous-system-control-of-heart-rate-2.png 3840w" style="color:transparent" width="1100"/></div><p class="text-center"><i><b>Nervous control of the heart rate by the cardioregulatory centre (also known as the cardiovascular control centre). Sympathetic neurones (red) will speed up the heart rate while parasympathetic neurones (blue) will slow the heart rate down</b></i></p></div></div></div>